# Exclude virtual environment
env/
**/env/

# Java/Maven builds
**/target/
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.settings/
**/*.class

# Python cache
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo

# Data files (uncomment if you want to exclude all data)
# **/data/raw/
# **/*.csv
# **/*.pkl
# **/*.keras
# **/*.json

# Models
**/models/saved_models/
**/models/scalers/
**/models/plots/

# IDE
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.iml
**/.DS_Store

# Logs
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
